sentences.english: Equipment nameplates will be bilingual, English and French.

sentences.english: In 1756 the Seven Years War between Britain and France broke out and Cook joined the navy.

sentences.english: Unquestionably, the united army is the chief criminal of the plunder.

sentences.english: The Tudor Dynasty was founded after the Hundred Years War and the Rose War.

sentences.english: In the Hundred Years War, England was defeated by France.
